nodes.text: Wkk'e was a female Mist-Weaver. Wkk'e was trapped inside an exogorth so she weaved herself into a cocoon made of Luminous Mist spun into resilient silk containing the hidden dimensions of the universe twisted into yarn strong enough to bind time. One eon was only one second to her inside the cocoon. She was then rescued by Luke Skywalker.
